        <Title>Citation</Title>
        <P1 id="article-1">
          <Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
          <P1para>
            <Text>This Order may be cited as the Historic Environment (Amendment) (Scotland) Act 2011 (Commencement <Abbreviation Expansion="Number">No.</Abbreviation><Character Name="NonBreakingSpace"/>1) Order 2011.</Text>
          </P1para>
        </P1>
