      <P1group>
        <Title>Appointed Day</Title>
        <P1 id="article-2">
          <Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
          <P1para>
            <P2 id="article-2-1">
              <Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
              <P2para>
                <Text>Subject to paragraph<Character Name="NonBreakingSpace"/>(2), the day appointed for the coming into force of the provisions of the Historic Environment (Amendment) (Scotland) Act 2011 specified in column<Character Name="NonBreakingSpace"/>1 of the Schedule (the subject matter of which is described in column<Character Name="NonBreakingSpace"/>2 of the Schedule) is 30th<Character Name="NonBreakingSpace"/>June 2011.</Text>
              </P2para>
            </P2>
            <P2 id="article-2-2">
              <Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
              <P2para>
                <Text>Where a purpose is specified in column<Character Name="NonBreakingSpace"/>3 of the Schedule in relation to any provision, that provision comes into force on 30th June 2011 for that purpose only.</Text>
              </P2para>
            </P2>
          </P1para>
        </P1>
      </P1group>
